Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:32.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}自分の過去に囚われ迷って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:37.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}そうじゃないよと　言い聞かせて　全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:42.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}自由に操れるかなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}分からないよと　空は霞んで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}正解はどこ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:53.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}僕の手のひらに　残る大事なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:57.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}忘れない記憶　何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:03.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}君を守り抜くと叫んで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:08.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}巻き戻しの中　掴んだ愛は　そう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}離しはしないから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:15.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}散りばめた想い　今一度きりの願いへ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:20.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}次への僕に　託したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:25.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}いつかの約束　光の道しるべになる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:36.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}誓いをさあ　君のため　最期まで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:41.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}涙さえ力に変えてきっと　描いていた望む未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}繋ぐよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:32.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}无法摆脱自己过去的束缚  迷失了前进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:37.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}还自欺述说那并不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:42.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}不知道这些是否能自由控制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}天色为何又如此朦胧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}答案又在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:53.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}双手还残留着有什么很重要的事尚未完成的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:57.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}这段记忆将尘封于心  永久保存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:03.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}誓要将你保护到底的决心已化作言语放声呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:08.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}回放逝去的倒带  把对你永恒的挚爱捧在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}定不会轻易放手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:15.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}这是最后一次请求  将这散落一地的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:20.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}托付给未来的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:25.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}曾经的约定  化作黎明的灯塔指引我前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:36.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我发誓将为了你支撑到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:41.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}连泪水也化作力量  一定会将心中描绘的所期待的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}与现实衔接
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:56.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:59.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:04.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:07.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:14.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:18.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:22.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:27.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:34.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:35.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:37.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:39.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:44.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:51.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:53.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:55.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:24:00.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.23,0:24:05.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:09.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.15,0:24:12.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.66,0:24:14.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.78,0:24:16.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.33,0:24:20.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.41,0:24:22.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:23.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:56.96,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:59.21,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:04.71,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:07.09,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:14.43,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失准的时钟 记录着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:18.44,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}散落满地的记忆之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:22.23,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:27.36,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看 却是那么轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:34.66,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:35.74,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望能与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:37.95,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:39.96,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:44.34,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不再失去曾经拥有的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:51.34,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我忘却自己的过去 重新开始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:53.55,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:55.47,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:24:00.10,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿那让你苦不堪言的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.23,0:24:05.44,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}会迎来完结的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:09.24,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我却要目送你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.15,0:24:12.53,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.66,0:24:14.66,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.78,0:24:16.53,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.33,0:24:20.37,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.41,0:24:22.46,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:23.71,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手迈进
